---+ uubeamer installation instructions

---++ Requirements
   * pgf >= 1.00 (http://www.sf.net/projects/pgf)
   * latex-beamer >= 3.06 (http://www.sf.net/projects/latex-beamer)

---++ Installation
   1. Download the package tar.gz and unpack it
   (tar zxvf uubeamer-<version>.tar.gz)
   2. To install it, put the uubeamer/ directory somewhere in 
   your TeX search path, e.g. under $HOMETEXMF/tex/latex/
   (i.e. $HOME/texmf/tex/latex/ on many Unix systems, or
   $HOME/Library/texmf/tex/latex/ on MacOS X).
   3. In your document, issue: \usetheme{uu}
   4. Compile your document: pdflatex yourpresentation.tex

More info at: http://www.math.uu.nl/people/dam/?UuBeamer
